metadata.title: Unotux 4 Piece Formal Boy Silver Gray Vest Set Suit 0 Month to 7 Years (XL:(18-24 Months))
features: Pants. Note: baby and toddler sized (S M L XL 2T 3T 4T) pants do not have a fly zipper and belt loops, only an elastic waistband.
Mini Matt Fabric is used on the back of vest
description: 1.The long white shirt is made out 35% cotton, 65% polyester fabric. 2. Matching solid color vest with cover buttons. 3. Matching pants, a hidden fly zipper in the front, belt loops and an adjustable elastic waistband. There are angled pockets on each side of the pants and two buttoned welt pockets on the back. Note: baby and toddler sized (S M L XL 2T 3T 4T) pants do not have a fly zipper and belt loops, only an elastic waistband. 4. A matching color necktie is included.
